      "text": [
        "655 - وَقَالَ أَبُو جَعْفَرٍ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «وَقْتُ اَلْمَغْرِبِ إِذَا غَابَ اَلْقُرْصُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.655 - Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) said:\n\"The time for Maghrib (evening prayer) begins when the disk of the sun disappears.\""
        ]
      }
    },
